===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|en|enm|*schrewe}}, from {{inh|en|ang|scrēawa|t=shrew|lit=biter}}, from {{der|en|gem-pro|*skrawwaz|t=thin; meagre; frail}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*(s)ker-|t=to cut; shorten; skimp}}. Cognates include {{etyl|goh|en}} {{m|goh|scrawaz||dwarf}}, {{etyl|no|en}} {{m|no|skrugg||dwarf}}.

